ustomer-Community-User-Guide&quot; rel=&quot;noopener noreferrer&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Overview of the Customer Community video&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;font-size: 10.5pt; color: rgb(9, 181, 209);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;Lastly Iâ€™m here to help&amp;nbsp;and&amp;nbsp;I&#39;d love to give you&amp;nbsp;some personal recommendations on what aspects of the community will bring you the best success in your&amp;nbsp;role,&amp;nbsp;so if you are interested&amp;nbsp;please let me know a bit more about what you do / what you need to achieve.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;Olivia McDonald&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;Customer Community Specialist&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://customercommunity.technologyonecorp.com/s/&quot; rel=&quot;noopener noreferrer&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 22px; color: rgb(9, 181, 209);&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Visit Customer Community Now&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</text>
